review_blob: Fantastic lager with a bit more "clackers" than a Samuel Smiths Pure Brewed Lager and other contemporaries.  Great pour and color and the aroma is solid.  Fantastice after taste to compliment its overall components.  Fantasitc brew!!

Malty with a slight hop undertone.  Very condensed but minimal head when poured, dont know if alititude affects this.  I like it better than some local dark ambers/bocks, but still could use something to hide the heavy alcohol scent.  Good overall brew.
